{"ts":"2026-06-25T23:35:08.989Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Analyzing Input Size**\n\nI've determined the input's size exceeds the recommended limit, which presents an intriguing challenge. I'm exploring file writing strategies. The `editor` tool seems capable of handling smaller files directly, but splitting the input might be necessary for larger ones.\n\n\n**Refining Component Design**\n\nI'm now focused on drastically reducing the component's character count. My current strategy involves compacting the patterns array and streamlining the component's structure to achieve a sleek, dense design. I'm aiming for a highly efficient and concise code version that can comfortably fit under the 6000-character limit, as this is essential for a great UX.\n\n\n**Constructing Draft Under Limit**\n\nI'm now implementing the compact code version. I'm focusing on reducing the patterns array and constructing a draft version with essential data. All requirements, including Case Studies and Business Outcomes, are present. I'm currently aiming for under 5000 characters by using brief outcomes, short labels, and brief layers to see how far I can go.\n\n\n**Modeling Compliance Patterns**\n\nI'm now modeling compliance patterns for enterprise cognitive routing. The goal is a representative pattern for multi-tier security evaluations of compliance audit logs. This involves improved compliance workflows by automated parsing and flagging, and faster decision-making via contextual flag justification. I'm focusing on \"Secure Gateway,\" \"Cognitive Router,\" \"Guardrail Node,\" and \"Ledger Backup\" layers.\n\n\n**Mapping Healthcare Knowledge**\n\nI'm now mapping secure medical record ingestion. My focus is real-time medical guideline query support via a clinical knowledge graph. I'm looking at index references across archives and research papers. Faster decision making is also a key objective, assisting doctors via indexing and clinical citations.\n\n\n**Defining Manufacturing AI**\n\nI'm now defining the structure for a manufacturing AI pattern, starting with SCADA Edge. I'm building out a system for an AI Factory, focusing on the key components and their interaction within the architecture. My latest work involves outlining the layers and log examples that represent the processes within the factory.\n\n\n**Designing Predictive Maintenance**\n\nI'm now designing a predictive maintenance pattern for an edge-based automation system. I'm focusing on streaming machinery diagnostics to predict and prevent outages. I'm implementing a gRPC receiver and a signal processor to handle high-frequency data. My current progress involves outlining the layers, outcomes, and technologies, including reduced manual effort and faster decision making.\n\n\n**Implementing Retail Automation**\n\nI'm now implementing the retail automation pattern, focusing on real-time agent routing for checkout inquiries. I'm building out layers for conversations and fulfillment services. I'm focusing on deflecting simple order lookup queries to expert agents. The current design includes CRM APIs for return verification. The key components include a fulfillment service and a conversation Ingress. My recent progress is in outlining these elements.\n\n\n**Refining Service Architecture**\n\nI'm now refining the service architecture for the retail automation pattern, specifically focusing on the components that handle real-time agent routing. I'm building out a comprehensive system, including: \"Feedback Unifier\", \"Intent Router\", \"Agent Core\", and \"CRM Gateway\". My current focus involves optimizing the interaction between these components to ensure a seamless flow of information and efficient query resolution. I'm also ensuring that transaction outcomes and conversation stats are saved to CRM loggers.\n\n\n**Evaluating Component Elements**\n\nI'm now evaluating the SVG and theme conditionals within the component to determine their contribution to the character count. My aim is to maintain visual representation while minimizing code size. I'm considering alternative approaches for conditional rendering and exploring ways to streamline these graphic elements.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-25T23:35:08.993Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"nv8cieb1","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/sections/ClientSuccessSection.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport SectionHeading from \"@/components/SectionHeading\";\n\ninterface Pattern {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  label: string;\n  color: string;\n  tags: string[];\n  longDesc: string;\n  outcomes: { theme: string; detail: string }[];\n  layers: { name: string; desc: string; tech: string[] }[];\n  logs: string[];\n}\n\nconst PATTERNS: Pattern[] = [\n  {\n    id: \"banking\",\n    name: \"Global Banking\",\n    label: \"Representative Pattern: Financial Compliance & Risk\",\n    color: \"#0186E4\",\n    tags: [\"Compliance\", \"Risk Ops\"],\n    longDesc: \"This representative pattern models enterprise cognitive routing coordinating multi-tier security evaluations for high-throughput compliance audit logs.\",\n    outcomes: [\n      { theme: \"improved compliance workflows\", detail: \"Automated parsing of local/international compliance standards to flag non-conforming items.\" },\n      { theme: \"faster decision making\", detail: \"Enabling rapid review workflows via contextual, automated flag justification generation.\" }\n    ],\n    layers: [\n      { name: \"Secure Gateway\", desc: \"Ingests transaction payloads encrypted with TLS 1.3.\", tech: [\"TLS 1.3\", \"JWT\"] },\n      { name: \"Cognitive Router\", desc: \"Routes files to regional security pipelines based on rules.\", tech: [\"GFF Custom Router\", \"vLLM\"] },\n      { name: \"Guardrail Node\", desc: \"Validates integrity metrics and redacts sensitive PII data.\", tech: [\"Guardrails SDK\", \"PII Redactor\"] },\n      { name: \"Ledger Backup\", desc: \"Persists compliant transaction receipts in deep safe storage.\", tech: [\"Temporal\", \"Cold Ledger\"] }\n    ],\n    logs: [\n      \"[00:01] SECURE INGESTION: Payload received via TLS 1.3.\",\n      \"[00:04] COMPLIANCE ROUTER: Parsing regulatory capital flows.\",\n      \"[00:07] SEMANTIC EVALUATION: Checked Capital Rule 104-B.\",\n      \"[00:10] GUARDRAIL NODE: Passed compliance check. Redacted PII.\",\n      \"[00:13] LEDGER BACKUP: Final trace committed to immutable backup.\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"healthcare\",\n    name: \"Clinical Intel\",\n    label: \"Representative Pattern: Healthcare Knowledge Operations\",\n    color: \"#E98828\",\n    tags: [\"Clinical\", \"Knowledge Graph\"],\n    longDesc: \"This representative pattern maps secure medical record ingestion into a clinical knowledge graph for real-time medical guidelines query support.\",\n    outcomes: [\n      { theme: \"better knowledge access\", detail: \"Providing instant index references across thousands of medical archives and research papers.\" },\n      { theme: \"faster decision making\", detail: \"Assisting doctors with instant medical guideline indexing and clinical citation highlights.\" }\n    ],\n    layers: [\n      { name: \"FHIR Ingest\", desc: \"Consolidates records and unstructured PDF documents.\", tech: [\"FHIR Schema\", \"Kafka\"] },\n      { name: \"Vector Pipeline\", desc: \"Generates high-dimensional clinical semantic coordinates.\", tech: [\"vLLM Embeddings\"] },\n      { name: \"Knowledge Database\", desc: \"Co-locates search coordinates inside pgvector and Neo4j.\", tech: [\"Neo4j\", \"pgvector\"] },\n      { name: \"Portal Gateway\", desc: \"Saves clinical insights with automated footnotes onto screen.\", tech: [\"React UI\", \"HIPAA Gateway\"] }\n    ],\n    logs: [\n      \"[00:01] INGESTION: Ingesting unstructured FHIR charts.\",\n      \"[00:04] VECTOR CONTEXT: Generating vector coordinates for guidelines.\",\n      \"[00:07] KNOWLEDGE GRAPH: Resolving entities inside Neo4j.\",\n      \"[00:10] HYBRID SEARCH: Performing joint query in graph database.\",\n      \"[00:13] CLINICAL PORTAL: Synthesized results render with citation links.\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"manufacturing\",\n    name: \"SCADA Edge\",\n    label: \"Representative Pattern: Manufacturing AI Factory\",\n    color: \"#E4000F\",\n    tags: [\"SCADA\", \"Supply Chain\"],\n    longDesc: \"This representative pattern represents edge-based automation streaming high-frequency machinery diagnostics to predict maintenance outages.\",\n    outcomes: [\n      { theme: \"reduced manual effort\", detail: \"Replacing periodic manual inspects with real-time continuous sensor anomalies monitoring.\" },\n      { theme: \"faster decision making\", detail: \"Dispatching replacement inventory orders to mechanical technicians instantly.\" }\n    ],\n    layers: [\n      { name: \"gRPC Receiver\", desc: \"Streams machinery vibration patterns directly from edge floor.\", tech: [\"gRPC Edge\", \"eBPF\"] },\n      { name: \"Signal Processor\", desc: \"Parses high-frequency telemetry cycles and removes SCADA noise.\", tech: [\"Redis Stream\", \"K8s Edge\"] },\n      { name: \"Predictive Agent\", desc: \"Forecasts hydraulic degradation factors using diagnostic loops.\", tech: [\"vLLM Interpreter\"] },\n      { name: \"ERP Dispatcher\", desc: \"Automates inventory reservations for scheduled mechanical repairs.\", tech: [\"Temporal\", \"ERP Webhook\"] }\n    ],\n    logs: [\n      \"[00:01] SCADA EDGE: Connected streaming telemetry client via gRPC.\",\n      \"[00:03] DEVIATION TRACE: Anomaly detected on hydraulic cycle 12.\",\n      \"[00:06] PREDICTION ENGINE: Forecasted structural repair window in 48h.\",\n      \"[00:09] LOGISTICS CORE: Reserving matching mechanical gaskets in ERP.\",\n      \"[00:12] DISPATCH WEBHOOK: Pushed automated repair schedule ticket.\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"retail\",\n    name: \"Retail Journeys\",\n    label: \"Representative Pattern: Retail Agent Operations\",\n    color: \"#009DFF\",\n    tags: [\"Commerce\", \"Personalization\"],\n    longDesc: \"This representative pattern details federated support agent routing, resolving checkout inquiries and maintaining multi-channel logs.\",\n    outcomes: [\n      { theme: \"improved employee experience\", detail: \"Empowering customer reps by deflecting simple order lookup queues to expert agents.\" },\n      { theme: \"reduced manual effort\", detail: \"Resolving return verification queries automatically through CRM APIs check.\" }\n    ],\n    layers: [\n      { name: \"Conversations Ingest\", desc: \"Unifies customer feedback across web, mobile and chat.\", tech: [\"WebSockets\", \"TLS 1.3\"] },\n      { name: \"Intent Router\", desc: \"Discovers user intent and dispatches chat to specialty sub-agents.\", tech: [\"GFF Router\", \"vLLM\"] },\n      { name: \"Agent Core\", desc: \"Co-ordinates agentic execution check against safety policies.\", tech: [\"Agentic SDK\", \"Guardrails\"] },\n      { name: \"CRM Gateway\", desc: \"Saves transaction outcomes and conversation stats to CRM loggers.\", tech: [\"OAuth CRM Hook\"] }\n    ],\n    logs: [\n      \"[00:01] WEB INTAKE: Session connected for billing modification query.\",\n      \"[00:03] COGNITION ROUTER: Classified user intent as 'Order return authorization'.\",\n      \"[00:06] INVENTORY AGENT: Verifying shipment dispatch timestamps.\",\n      \"[00:09] AGENT CORE: Generated returning mailing barcode automatically.\",\n      \"[00:12] CRM OUTBOUND: Syncing resolved transaction logs to database.\"\n    ]\n  }\n];\n\nfunction OutcomeIcon({ theme }: { theme: string }) {\n  if (theme.includes(\"compliance\")) return <svg className=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth={1.5}><path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" /></svg>;\n  if (theme.includes(\"decision\")) return <svg className=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth={1.5}><path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\" /></svg>;\n  if (theme.includes(\"manual\")) return <svg className=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth={1.5}><path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065-2.924-1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z\" /><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\" /></svg>;\n  if (theme.includes(\"knowledge\")) return <svg className=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth={1.5}><path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253\" /></svg>;\n  return <svg className=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth={1.5}><path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" /></svg>;\n}\n\nexport default function ClientSuccessSection() {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<string>(\"banking\");\n  const [isPlaying, setIsPlaying] = useState<boolean>(true);\n  const [progress, setProgress] = useState<number>(0);\n  const timelineRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);\n\n  const activePattern = PATTERNS.find((p) => p.id === activeTab) || PATTERNS[0];\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    let interval: any = null;\n    if (isPlaying) {\n      interval = setInterval(() => {\n        setProgress((prev) => {\n          if (prev >= 100) return 0;\n          return prev + 1;\n        });\n      }, 120);\n    }\n    return () => {\n      if (interval) clearInterval(interval);\n    };\n  }, [isPlaying]);\n\n  const activeStep = Math.min(3, Math.floor(progress / 25));\n  const activeLayer = activePattern.layers[activeStep];\n\n  const handleTimelineClick = (e: React.MouseEvent<HTMLDivElement>) => {\n    if (!timelineRef.current) return;\n    const rect = timelineRef.current.getBoundingClientRect();\n    const clickX = e.clientX - rect.left;\n    setProgress(Math.max(0, Math.min(100, (clickX / rect.width) * 100)));\n  };\n\n  const selectTab = (id: string) => {\n    setActiveTab(id);\n    setProgress(0);\n    setIsPlaying(true);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <motion.section\n      initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n      whileInView={{ opacity: 1 }}\n      viewport={{ once: true }}\n      transition={{ duration: 0.8 }}\n      className=\"w-full bg-[#020202] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-16 lg:py-32 py-20 relative overflow-hidden border-t border-white/5\"\n      id=\"client-success\"\n    >\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style={{ backgroundImage: `radial-gradient(circle at 50% 10%, ${activePattern.color}15 0%, transparent 60%)` }} />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto relative z-10\">\n        <SectionHeading\n          title={\n            <h2 className=\"text-[32px] sm:text-[44px] leading-none font-bold text-center uppercase text-white tracking-widest\">\n              CLIENT <span style={{ color: activePattern.color }} className=\"transition-colors duration-500\">SUCCESS</span>\n            </h2>\n          }\n          titleClassName=\"text-center\"\n          dividerWidthClassName=\"w-[300px]\"\n        />\n\n        <p className=\"mt-6 text-center text-[15px] sm:text-[17px] text-[#A0A0A0] max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n          We construct robust intelligence layers. Explore our blueprints and active telemetry simulations below.\n        </p>\n\n        {/* Disclaimer label */}\n        <div className=\"mt-8 max-w-xl mx-auto bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-center\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] tracking-widest font-bold uppercase text-white/50 block mb-0.5\">REPRESENTATIVE PATTERNS ONLY</span>\n          <p className=\"text-[12px] text-white/80 font-mono leading-relaxed\">\n            Architectural configurations and outcomes are anonymized to protect enterprise secrets. No fake names or numbers.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Tabs Control */}\n        <div className=\"mt-12 flex justify-center\">\n          <div className=\"inline-flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 p-1.5 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 max-w-full overflow-x-auto justify-center\">\n            {PATTERNS.map((p) => {\n              const isActive = p.id === activeTab;\n              return (\n                <button\n                  key={p.id}\n                  onClick={() => selectTab(p.id)}\n                  className={`relative flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[13px] font-bold tracking-wide transition-all uppercase whitespace-nowrap ${isActive ? \"text-white\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/70\"}`}\n                >\n                  {isActive && (\n                    <motion.div\n                      layoutId=\"activeTabGlow\"\n                      className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-xl border\"\n                      style={{ borderColor: p.color, background: `${p.color}08` }}\n                      transition={{ type: \"spring\", stiffness: 380, damping: 30 }}\n                    />\n                  )}\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5\" style={{ color: isActive ? p.color : \"inherit\" }}>PATTERN</span>\n                  {p.name}\n                </button>\n              );\n            })}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Left and Right Grid */}\n        <div className=\"mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n          \n          {/* Left Block: Description & Outcomes */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6\">\n            <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-8\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white/40 block mb-2 font-mono\">{activePattern.label}</span>\n              <h3 className=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight\">{activePattern.name} Architecture</h3>\n              <p className=\"mt-4 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-[#A0A0A0]\">{activePattern.longDesc}</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-4\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-white/50 px-2 font-mono\">Business Outcomes Focus</span>\n              \n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-4\">\n                {activePattern.outcomes.map((o, idx) => (\n                  <div key={idx} className=\"group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 p-5 flex gap-4 items-start\">\n                    <div className=\"absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-[3px] rounded-l-2xl\" style={{ backgroundColor: activePattern.color }} />\n                    <div className=\"p-2 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/5 flex-shrink-0\" style={{ color: activePattern.color }}>\n                      <OutcomeIcon theme={o.theme} />\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40 block mb-1\">Outcome Theme</span>\n                      <h4 className=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-white capitalize\">{o.theme}</h4>\n                      <p className=\"mt-1 text-[13px] text-[#A0A0A0] leading-relaxed\">{o.detail}</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Right Block: Blueprint & Telemetry console */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-6 w-full\">\n            \n            {/* Blueprint */}\n            <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-8\">\n              <div className=\"flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center gap-2 mb-6 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/40 block uppercase\">SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE</span>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mt-0.5\">PROCESS PIPELINE</h4>\n                </div>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono px-2 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-white/70\">Click stage node to jump</span>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Pipeline Row */}\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n                {activePattern.layers.map((layer, idx) => {\n                  const isActive = idx === activeStep;\n                  return (\n                    <button\n                      key={idx}\n                      onClick={() => setProgress(idx * 25 + 5)}\n                      className={`relative flex flex-col text-left p-3.5 rounded-xl border transition-all ${isActive ? \"bg-white/[0.04]\" : \"bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] border-white/5\"}`}\n                      style={{\n                        borderColor: isActive ? activePattern.color : \"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)\",\n                        boxShadow: isActive ? `${activePattern.color}15 0px 4px 20px` : \"none\"\n                      }}\n                    >\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-1 w-full\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30\">0{idx + 1}</span>\n                        {isActive && <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\"><span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full opacity-75\" style={{ backgroundColor: activePattern.color }} /><span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2\" style={{ backgroundColor: activePattern.color }} /></span>}\n                      </div>\n                      <h5 className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-white mt-2 truncate w-full\">{layer.name}</h5>\n                    </button>\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Inspector details */}\n              <div className=\"mt-5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] min-h-[110px]\">\n                <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-1\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/30\">Active Blueprint Layer</span>\n                  <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\">\n                    {activeLayer.tech.map((t) => (\n                      <span key={t} className=\"text-[9px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/60\">{t}</span>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <h5 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-white mt-1\">{activeLayer.name}</h5>\n                <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#A0A0A0] mt-1.5 leading-relaxed\">{activeLayer.desc}</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Simulated telemetry walkthrough video console */}\n            <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-md overflow-hidden flex flex-col\">\n              <div className=\"px-5 py-4 border-b border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between bg-white/[0.01]\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                  <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\">\n                    {isPlaying ? <><span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75\" /><span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500\" /></> : <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-white/40\" />}\n                  </span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 uppercase tracking-widest\">WALKTHROUGH TELEMETRY (VIDEO FEED)</span>\n                </div>\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-white/50\">1080P TELEMETRY</span>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"p-5 bg-black min-h-[190px] font-mono text-[11px] sm:text-[12px] flex flex-col justify-between relative\">\n                <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#ffffff03_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px] pointer-events-none\" />\n\n                {!isPlaying && (\n                  <div onClick={() => setIsPlaying(true)} className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/75 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer z-20 backdrop-blur-[1px]\">\n                    <div className=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[16px] text-white pl-0.5\">▶</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-white/50 tracking-wider\">RESUME TELEMETRY PLAYBACK</span>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n\n                <div className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col gap-2.5\">\n                  <AnimatePresence>\n                    {activePattern.logs.map((log, idx) => {\n                      if (idx > activeStep) return null;\n                      return (\n                        <motion.div key={idx} initial={{ opacity: 0, x: -5 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }} exit={{ opacity: 0 }} transition={{ duration: 0.3 }} className=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-white/80\">\n                          <span style={{ color: activePattern.color }} className=\"font-bold flex-shrink-0\">▶</span>\n                          <span className=\"leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap\">{log}</span>\n                        </motion.div>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                  </AnimatePresence>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"relative z-10 mt-4 flex items-center justify-between text-white/30 text-[10px] pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                    <span className=\"inline-block w-1.5 h-3 animate-pulse\" style={{ backgroundColor: activePattern.color }} />\n                    <span>SYSTEM RUNTIME ACTIVE...</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <span>NODE {activeStep + 1} ACTIVE</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Video Player Controls */}\n              <div className=\"px-5 py-4 border-t border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] flex flex-col gap-3\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 w-full\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">00:0{Math.floor(progress / 7).toString()}</span>\n                  \n                  <div ref={timelineRef} onClick={handleTimelineClick} className=\"h-1.5 flex-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full overflow-hidden cursor-pointer relative group\">\n                    <div className=\"absolute inset-y-0 left-0 transition-all rounded-full\" style={{ width: `${progress}%`, backgroundColor: activePattern.color }} />\n                    <div className=\"absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity pointer-events-none\" style={{ left: `calc(${progress}% - 6px)`, backgroundColor: \"#fff\" }} />\n                  </div>\n\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">00:15</span>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n                    <button onClick={() => setIsPlaying(!isPlaying)} className=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 text-white transition-all text-xs font-bold min-w-[65px]\">\n                      {isPlaying ? \"⏸ PAUSE\" : \"▶ PLAY\"}\n                    </button>\n                    <button onClick={() => setProgress(0)} className=\"px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 hover:border-white/15 text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-all text-[10px]\">\n                      RESET\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/40 uppercase\">TELEMETRY STREAM SYNCHRONIZED</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </motion.section>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
